Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.36,0:00:02.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,《超感警探》前情提要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.54,0:00:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十年前  被称作血腥约翰的连环杀手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.39,0:00:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀害了我的妻子和女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.45,0:00:15.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自那以后我们一直在追捕他
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.32,0:00:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们自称为"布莱克组织"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.77,0:00:19.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,组织里还有些什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.54,0:00:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警察  法官  联调局探员
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.54,0:00:24.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何一个有秘密需要掩盖的执法人员
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.23,0:00:26.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个腐败警察的秘密组织
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.28,0:00:28.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血腥约翰是成员之一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.03,0:00:32.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基拉·汀斯利死之前跟我说了件事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.26,0:00:34.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她告诉我杀她的人  也就是血腥约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.74,0:00:36.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个纹身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.55,0:00:38.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左臂上有三个点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.69,0:00:40.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底谁是血腥约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.91,0:00:42.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我们很高兴地宣布
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.16,0:00:45.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们终于确认了他的身份与面目
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.71,0:00:49.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,执法部门负责人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.03,0:00:51.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盖尔·伯特仑局长  就是血腥约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.94,0:00:55.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我手里有一份
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.45,0:00:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联邦法官签署的令状
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.95,0:01:00.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联调局将立即关闭你们部门
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.97,0:01:03.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了  这里没我们的事儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.74,0:01:06.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会放弃  我不信你会放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.37,0:01:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前的情况我们已经无法掌控了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.46,0:01:10.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保持联络  好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.00,0:01:13.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的一切  我很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.34,0:01:43.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里斯本
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.86,0:01:46.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高兴你能过来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.51,0:01:47.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上塞车
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.77,0:01:49.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.91,0:01:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一有空就过来见你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.49,0:01:54.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.52,0:02:08.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.26,0:02:14.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情况真是一团糟  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.41,0:02:17.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.63,0:02:19.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-听着  我觉得我们...  -一会儿有你说的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.68,0:02:23.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.43,0:02:27.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们现在肯定都很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.65,0:02:28.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.19,0:02:31.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道接下来会发生什么事  对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.64,0:02:33.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-探员  -所以我来说明下接下来会发生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.50,0:02:38.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来的几天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.83,0:02:40.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会找你们每个人谈话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.23,0:02:42.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,单独谈话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.09,0:02:47.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们有权委托律师或工会代表随行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.46,0:02:49.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由你们自己选择
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.23,0:02:50.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们为何需要律师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.58,0:02:55.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从我们的角度来看看这事  金宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.04,0:02:58.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的上司伯特仑是个罪犯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.03,0:03:01.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以有可能你们也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.10,0:03:05.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会非常仔细地审视你们每个人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.36,0:03:07.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你们有任何
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.92,0:03:10.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要一点点可疑的举动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.91,0:03:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都会发现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.76,0:03:14.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后起诉你们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.26,0:03:17.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了  除非
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.95,0:03:22.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们能够配合  那我们会非常非常满意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.51,0:03:25.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样你们就有点回旋的余地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.77,0:03:33.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fad(400,400)\fs18\pos(194.4,267.2)}加州  萨克拉门托  富兰克林区
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.56,0:03:35.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联调局展开一场全球缉凶行动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.59,0:03:38.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通缉著名的萨克拉门托执法部门官员
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.37,0:03:39.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盖尔·伯特仑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.47,0:03:40.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联调局方面证实
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.66,0:03:44.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据信伯特仑就是臭名昭著的连环杀手血腥约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.91,0:03:46.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他因在整个加利福尼亚州中心地带
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.72,0:03:48.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犯下一系列恐怖凶案而被通缉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.65,0:04:08.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伙计
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.83,0:04:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:19.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这有公用电话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.70,0:04:20.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.80,0:04:25.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.60,0:04:36.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿里  你好啊  给我张六合彩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.12,0:04:38.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一根菠萝味雪茄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.69,0:04:42.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六合彩  雪茄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.55,0:05:03.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.77,0:05:04.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  派翠克
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.97,0:05:07.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用不着捏着嗓子讲话  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.62,0:05:08.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:10.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.12,0:05:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉真奇怪啊  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.89,0:05:14.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们上次...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.28,0:05:22.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,举起手来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.44,0:05:32.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.44,0:05:36.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.71,0:05:37.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.74,0:05:38.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别客气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.54,0:05:40.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  伯特仑  还在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.30,0:06:26.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人  长官
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.49,0:06:29.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:47.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.68,0:06:51.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你问的是简  那我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.59,0:06:53.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去楼上找过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.16,0:06:54.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.09,0:06:58.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也许还没听说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:07:00.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大约一小时前  盖尔·伯特仑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.97,0:07:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在萨城东区的一个加油站杀了一个警察
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:05.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.56,0:07:09.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你听说了伯特仑当时在加油站做什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.39,0:07:10.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.85,0:07:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在打公用电话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.28,0:07:14.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猜猜他打给了谁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.37,0:07:16.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜是简
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.82,0:07:19.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  那他在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.01,0:07:20.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.71,0:07:22.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为你清楚得很
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.20,0:07:25.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没法左右你的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.11,0:07:29.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为你的男朋友和一名危险的逃犯勾结
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.49,0:07:33.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为他已经深陷布莱克组织中无法自拔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.74,0:07:35.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.83,0:07:37.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是  他也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.50,0:07:40.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简无法阻止打给他的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.90,0:07:42.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且他也不是我的男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.91,0:07:44.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太遗憾了  特蕾莎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.83,0:07:47.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人人都说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.68,0:07:49.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你曾是个好警察
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.46,0:07:50.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在依旧是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.01,0:08:07.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头儿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.37,0:08:10.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑞斯比
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:12.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周围安全吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.52,0:08:13.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  你们在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.69,0:08:20.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们听说了伯特仑今早干的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.22,0:08:21.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说联调局的人在找我们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.08,0:08:24.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以现在是怎样  你们就躲在停车场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.59,0:08:26.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我们不是躲起来  只是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.60,0:08:27.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,低调行事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:28.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们暂时还安全
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.39,0:08:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少现在还没有下达对我们的逮捕令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.77,0:08:31.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们迟早会的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.75,0:08:32.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.09,0:08:33.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别问
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.84,0:08:34.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她刚已经问了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.55,0:08:37.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.74,0:08:39.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今加调局已经不复存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.50,0:08:42.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只能靠自己了  你们得保护好自己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.44,0:08:45.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不知道简在哪里  他在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.61,0:08:48.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不想知道  明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.67,0:08:49.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白  头儿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.04,0:08:52.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-明白  头儿  -明白  头儿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.61,0:08:53.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.14,0:08:57.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我已经不是你们的头儿了  关键就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.25,0:08:58.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只能靠自己
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.25,0:09:01.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.90,0:09:02.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那他在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.69,0:09:07.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fad(400,400)\fs18\pos(191.4,278.4)}加州  萨克拉门托  威廉兰德公园
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.50,0:09:18.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你被通缉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.03,0:09:20.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.68,0:09:24.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说真的  艾伯特给你下了逮捕令
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.02,0:09:25.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是第一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.04,0:09:29.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你到底要不要告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.81,0:09:32.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦对  伯特仑打给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.02,0:09:33.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.42,0:09:34.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.21,0:09:36.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管他想说什么  他那时都没来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.10,0:09:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么他还在城里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.87,0:09:41.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他想做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.17,0:09:43.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜他会很快再打来告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:45.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的手机不安全  联调局...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.32,0:09:47.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  他们装了窃听
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.22,0:09:48.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他们还没追踪到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:50.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他们追踪到了  我现在就早该被捕了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.92,0:09:53.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许如此  但他们早晚会追踪到你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.39,0:09:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.38,0:09:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在伯特仑打来之前我不能扔掉手机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.56,0:09:59.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以事情就悬在这了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.24,0:10:01.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他到底想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.44,0:10:02.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.56,0:10:03.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯特仑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.11,0:10:04.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.72,0:10:06.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在闪烁其词
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.17,0:10:10.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鸟的眼睛圆又亮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.12,0:10:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,《小恐龙》[系列童书]  你知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.33,0:10:13.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.81,0:10:16.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你很清楚他的意图
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.46,0:10:17.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他到底想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.55,0:10:24.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-喂  -很抱歉我那时不得不挂电话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.95,0:10:26.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天实在太忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.64,0:10:28.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系  这个电话不安全
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.94,0:10:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上再打给你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.71,0:10:31.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.65,0:10:33.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.80,0:10:34.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.71,0:10:37.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.79,0:10:39.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出一百块换你的手机  行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.97,0:10:40.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.69,0:10:44.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两百块换你的手机
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.28,0:10:47.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么骗局吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.42,0:10:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是骗局
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.35,0:10:51.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三百块  外加
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.42,0:10:53.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一部替代机
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.94,0:10:55.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.47,0:10:58.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥们  我一会儿再打给你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.74,0:11:00.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交易愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.37,0:11:02.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢了  伙计
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.21,0:11:06.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他刚才到底说了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.36,0:11:10.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得我们应该见面好好谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.53,0:11:12.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-就我们俩  -就像约会一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.50,0:11:15.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.19,0:11:17.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.46,0:11:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着  游戏结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.87,0:11:25.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得说你我确实不分伯仲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.68,0:11:27.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然现在一切都结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.81,0:11:29.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的觉得我们应该好好谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.32,0:11:32.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停战  不带武器  不玩花招
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.27,0:11:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.73,0:11:36.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后各行其道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.30,0:11:38.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谈谈  谈什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.21,0:11:41.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谈谈这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.88,0:11:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我们都需要有个了结  不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.16,0:11:47.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在今天  现在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:49.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我时间有点紧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.83,0:11:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么知道能否相信你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.32,0:11:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都到现在了就别胆小了  派翠克
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.04,0:11:57.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有那么多机会杀你  却都没下手  不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.78,0:12:00.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  时间  地点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.88,0:12:01.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.07,0:12:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,半小时后弗里蒙特公园的喷泉边见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.75,0:12:07.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  我不知道那个地方  中央汽车站见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.89,0:12:09.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-北入口  -不行  那里人太多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.81,0:12:10.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且警察太多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.19,0:12:12.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道亚历山大公墓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.02,0:12:15.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.67,0:12:18.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西门那边有个小教堂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.19,0:12:20.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行啊  半小时之后见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.62,0:12:22.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别迟到  我不能待太久
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.43,0:12:23.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,半小时之后见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.17,0:12:27.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.81,0:12:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他想见我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.46,0:12:31.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是个陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:33.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.21,0:12:35.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你准备怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.00,0:12:37.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去见他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.90,0:12:38.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.91,0:12:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我  我知道自己在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.11,0:12:44.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简  别去  你想想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.75,0:12:47.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联调局马上就要抓到伯特仑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.19,0:12:49.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想他落在联调局手上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.04,0:12:52.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道这一天早晚会来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.15,0:12:55.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是今天了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.09,0:12:57.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我和你一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.12,0:12:58.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  我不想让你牵扯进来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.60,0:13:00.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牵扯  我早就深陷其中了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.14,0:13:01.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能再这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.52,0:13:07.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要借你的枪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.82,0:13:09.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的枪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.78,0:13:10.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  你的枪  我不会开枪的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.92,0:13:12.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是壮壮胆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.38,0:13:16.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特蕾莎  请你相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.33,0:13:17.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.49,0:13:33.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.15,0:13:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.64,0:13:57.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:45.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,疑犯逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.57,0:15:25.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,负责人呢  艾伯特在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:27.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跪下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.04,0:15:28.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把手举到我能看见的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.69,0:15:30.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾伯特在哪儿  我必须得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.41,0:15:33.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  淡定点  伙计们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.84,0:15:35.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他又不是阿尔·卡彭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.84,0:15:35.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}著名黑帮老大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.41,0:15:37.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾伯特  请听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.71,0:15:40.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看得出来你是个正人君子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.01,0:15:42.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以我的名誉发誓  我一小时之后就回去自首
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.83,0:15:46.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是现在  我...  我要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.50,0:15:48.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.77,0:15:52.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.76,0:15:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别别别  告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:55.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.86,0:15:57.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要干什么  你需要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.95,0:15:59.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你需要一小时
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.86,0:16:01.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.53,0:16:02.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.44,0:16:05.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去见谁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.61,0:16:07.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.71,0:16:10.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那回局里说怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.27,0:16:15.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事  让她过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.45,0:16:18.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  里斯本女士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.27,0:16:20.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是咱们两个警察间帮个忙  艾伯特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.40,0:16:23.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放他走  我发誓到时候一定把他带回来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.63,0:16:26.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.06,0:16:30.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们到底有什么紧急的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:34.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是跟伯特仑有约吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.15,0:16:36.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.79,0:16:38.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了  艾伯特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.41,0:16:39.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联调局  退后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.50,0:16:42.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-加调局  你给我退后  -怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.82,0:16:45.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放他走  艾伯特  他什么也没做错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.91,0:16:47.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊  各位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.62,0:16:49.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高兴见到你们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:53.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本来不想打击你们的  但加调局已经不存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.20,0:16:55.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的警徽就是个玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.61,0:16:58.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你们只是在假扮警察
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.05,0:17:00.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随你怎么说  放他走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.85,0:17:04.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是缠上我了是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.97,0:17:06.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缠上联调局了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.48,0:17:08.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说你是真的联调局探员  有什么证据
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.61,0:17:10.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  你们也许是布莱克组织的成员
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.20,0:17:11.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是没可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.76,0:17:13.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.76,0:17:15.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿出证明来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.53,0:17:16.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的手下里德·史密斯就是其中之一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.96,0:17:18.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么不可能是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.46,0:17:21.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我们怎么知道简会不会有危险
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.46,0:17:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太荒唐了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:23.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 艾伯特探员
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.77,0:17:25.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在确保他的安全之前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.61,0:17:28.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护好他是我们的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.14,0:17:29.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放他走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.62,0:17:33.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样  别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.56,0:17:34.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的  放下枪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.95,0:17:37.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位都放下枪  没必要起冲突
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.02,0:17:38.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.84,0:17:40.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.43,0:17:41.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开我的车
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.65,0:17:46.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长官
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.76,0:17:47.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系  让他走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.65,0:17:53.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.21,0:18:06.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.28,0:18:08.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他走了  就没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.56,0:18:12.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逮捕他们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.18,0:18:16.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你们的枪都放到地上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.45,0:18:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.89,0:18:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照他说的做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.17,0:18:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去追踪里斯本探员的车
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.70,0:18:34.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  长官
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.41,0:18:37.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在我车上装了追踪器
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.58,0:18:39.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不我们怎么能找到简
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.42,0:18:42.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过认识你们这些人我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.15,0:18:43.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我知道你们早晚要出篓子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.70,0:18:45.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能省我不少事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.82,0:18:47.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这不就照做了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.22,0:18:49.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.20,0:18:51.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逮捕她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.65,0:18:56.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.31,0:19:40.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还没准备好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.37,0:19:41.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.56,0:19:48.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:51.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧瞧这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.93,0:19:53.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.91,0:19:57.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能帮我看会儿车吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.18,0:19:58.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了  会看好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.91,0:20:00.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.03,0:20:04.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.01,0:20:08.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  伙计  别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.40,0:20:37.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.77,0:20:44.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉麻烦你了  女士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.60,0:20:46.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说来话长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.01,0:20:48.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你愿不愿意载我一程
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.39,0:21:16.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是四队  我们发现目标车辆了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.59,0:21:18.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停在第五大道和谢尔曼街交会处
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.82,0:21:22.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退后  先退后  他们可能就在那儿接头
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.05,0:21:26.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.66,0:21:29.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四队  什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.75,0:21:34.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四队  回答  该死的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.58,0:21:36.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头儿  里斯本车里就几个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.07,0:21:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简不在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.45,0:21:39.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有发现简  重复  我们没发现简
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.64,0:21:41.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是否收...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.52,0:21:46.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再越错越多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.19,0:21:48.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他去哪儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.35,0:21:49.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.66,0:21:54.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是不见棺材不落泪是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.82,0:21:57.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长官  我们真的不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.12,0:22:13.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长官  你居然还叫他长官
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.08,0:22:14.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别激动  "头号公敌"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.08,0:22:14.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}约翰.迪林杰是萧条时期联调局追捕的最著名的黑帮头目  曾两度越狱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.56,0:22:16.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在是阶下囚  还是识相点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.44,0:22:19.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛  你以为能弄到个好点的牢房
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.63,0:22:31.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢[西语]  奥雷利奥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.52,0:22:33.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别客气  祝你好运[西语]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.28,0:22:59.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fn方正粗倩_GBK\c&H181417&\fs12\frz-1\b1\fry5\b0\pos(78,97.6)}安琪拉·萝斯金·简
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.28,0:22:59.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fn方正粗倩_GBK\c&H181417&\fs12\frz-1\b1\fry5\b0\pos(316.2,99)}夏洛特·安妮·简
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.09,0:23:17.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派翠克
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.18,0:23:24.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得先得搜搜你身上有没有武器
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.43,0:23:26.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后你才能进去  把手举起来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.81,0:23:40.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试下也无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.47,0:23:42.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.56,0:23:52.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派翠克
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.32,0:23:56.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你这么准时
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.71,0:23:59.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你骗了我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.80,0:24:02.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不也是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.80,0:24:05.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还真是俩无赖  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.33,0:24:10.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保证  这是最后一次骗你了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.85,0:24:13.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先说正事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.50,0:24:16.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和联调局犯了个严重的错误
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.34,0:24:19.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是血腥约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.08,0:24:37.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.52,0:24:40.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是血腥约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.62,0:24:42.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉让你失望了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.01,0:24:43.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我只是布莱克组织
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.66,0:24:44.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一员卑微走卒罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.89,0:24:47.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血腥约翰可是高层
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.63,0:24:52.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是很相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.31,0:24:55.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信不信是你的权利  但
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.30,0:24:57.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我说的是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.06,0:24:59.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的结论都是错的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.44,0:25:05.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么谁是血腥约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.31,0:25:06.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.38,0:25:10.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.31,0:25:11.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.45,0:25:15.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,组织严格遵循的原则是只须知道必需的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.72,0:25:17.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假设你说的是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.19,0:25:19.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我们完全可以在电话里说
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.61,0:25:21.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果我们在电话里说
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.27,0:25:23.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你  你可能就不会来见我了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.87,0:25:24.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.99,0:25:26.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我接到命令要打电话给你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.93,0:25:30.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉你游戏结束  安排和你见面
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.04,0:25:31.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.00,0:25:33.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要我过来
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.69,0:25:39.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你千万不要以为
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.11,0:25:41.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我乐意这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.04,0:25:44.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,组织不想有遗留问题
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.42,0:25:47.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们讨厌留下把柄
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.33,0:25:48.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.82,0:25:56.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动手吧  奥斯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.61,0:25:58.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别  别  听着  听着
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.79,0:26:01.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们谈谈  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.25,0:26:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很抱歉  这不是我能决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.47,0:26:07.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都很喜欢你  派翠克
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.05,0:26:11.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别  别  不需要这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.35,0:26:13.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.37,0:26:17.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.85,0:26:23.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  奥斯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.16,0:26:27.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以出去等着了  就...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.80,0:26:29.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确保没人来打扰我们
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.99,0:26:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  派翠克
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.18,0:26:45.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.98,0:27:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.46,0:27:07.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格蕾斯  你在干
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.01,0:27:09.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你  别这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.75,0:27:10.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还不如周呢
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.51,0:27:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们必须告诉我们到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.14,0:27:14.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们不需要做任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.12,0:27:16.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也什么都做不了  行行好就放松点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.46,0:27:18.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放松  我怎么放松得下来
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.51,0:27:20.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有时候表现的好像你很享受无助感
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.26,0:27:22.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  我收回  别放松
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.14,0:27:23.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就用额头把车窗撞破
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.34,0:27:24.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就可以跳车跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.42,0:27:26.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伙计们  团结一点好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.37,0:27:28.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.94,0:27:31.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"抱歉"
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.97,0:27:35.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫林斯  你是本地人  对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.41,0:27:36.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  长官  林肯高地的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.68,0:27:38.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-给我弄一张萨克拉门托的地图  -是  长官
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.44,0:27:40.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,车里的电脑上就有
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.27,0:27:41.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纸质地图
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.67,0:27:45.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纸质  地图
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.04,0:27:47.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点去找
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.94,0:27:51.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有纸质地图吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.37,0:27:54.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派翠克  终于又见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.39,0:28:00.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.60,0:28:02.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说他聪明他又傻
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.37,0:28:06.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他从来没想到
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.47,0:28:09.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是布莱克组织的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.64,0:28:10.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么要杀他
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.84,0:28:14.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个人都认为他是血腥约翰  不是吗
